<br>
I'd like a few people who were here when there was no rotation to post some stories of what it was like to go after Trak or VS.  The racing each other the training the KSing, etc.<br>
<br>
All you people saying it should be FFA think about something.  There are 4-7 guilds capable of killing said mobs.  Everybody knows said mobs spawn dates.  All guilds STILL want said mob.<br>
<br>
So what FFA will stem to is 4-7 guilds and a bunch of other people hoping to get in on the &quot;phat *cough haha* lootz&quot; racing to the spawn.  Ugly trains, KSing, etc.  GM will get involved some guilds might get disbanded (happened on bertoxx).<br>
<br>
All this talk about the little guilds getting left out etc...If it is so easy to do VS in house w/ 2 groups toss a group together and ask for a shot at VS.  Maybe a guild who has a spot will let you go.  Then you get in on rotation.<br>
<br>
Granted there is no EULA agreement on taking turns.  It is the people who play the game who make the game great, not Verant.  They wouldn't have a clue what great is.  If this were a single player game I would have moved on after a week.  Not the 2 years I've been playing. <p><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5"><tr><td valign="top"><font face="Arial Black" size="2"><A HREF="mailto:asicuseq@hotmail.com">Asicus Freakay</A><BR><b><i>52nd</i></b> Hafring Champion</font></td><td valign="top"><font face="Arial Black" size="2"><A HREF="mailto:asicuseq@hotmail.com">Aticus Freakay</A><BR><b><i>45th</i></b> Leezard Shaman</font></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><font face="Arial Narrow" size="1">Alfinius Freakay</A><BR><b><i>55th</i></b>  Evoker<BR>Bertoxxulous Server (retired)</font></td><td valign="top"><font face="Arial Narrow" size="1">Joniton Freakay</A><BR><b><i>53rd</i></b>  Illusionist<BR>Bertoxxulous Server (retired)</font></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showPrevMessage?topicID=906.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showNextMessage?topicID=906.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=906.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/es/themes/default/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.emailToFriend?topicID=906.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.threadControl?topicID=906.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.c